# Onboarding Experience PRD

## Overview

New users land on the onboarding flow immediately after signup. The goal is to:
1. Collect user info (who they are)
2. Collect & verify business information (AI-powered data gathering)
3. Define what support they need (universal framing)
4. Review and launch their first opportunity listing

Users who haven't completed onboarding see a blurred campaign table (3 visible rows) with a "Complete Setup" CTA.

