## Technical Notes

### Data Gathering Approach

**AI-Powered (Primary):**
- Feed URLs to LLM with web browsing capability
- Or use Firecrawl / similar AI scraping service
- Extract: name, logo, description, category signals, social metrics

**API (For proprietary data):**
- Ahrefs API → Domain Rating
- Can run async if slow (show "Pending" then update)

**Fallback:**
- If AI fails, show empty form
- User fills in manually
- Still works, just less magic

### AI Prompts Needed
1. **Company analysis** — Extract structured data from URLs
2. **Anonymized company summary** — Generate public-facing description
3. **Listing title** — Generate compelling, anonymized title
4. **Listing summary** — Generate anonymized opportunity description

### Data Model

```typescript
interface User {
  id: string;
  email: string;
  full_name: string;
  position: string;
  onboarding_completed: boolean;
  onboarding_step: number; // 1-4
}

interface Company {
  id: string;
  user_id: string;
  
  // Private
  name: string;
  website: string;
  one_liner: string;
  
  // Public
  anonymized_summary: string;
  category: string;
  logo_url: string;
  
  // Metrics
  domain_rating: number;
  reach: number;
  
  // Sources
  socials: {
    linkedin?: string;
    twitter?: string;
    instagram?: string;
    newsletter?: string;
  };
}

interface Listing {
  id: string;
  company_id: string;
  
  // Private
  original_context: string;
  
  // Public (anonymized)
  title: string;
  summary: string;
  
  // Structured
  partnership_types: string[]; // 'sponsorship' | 'collaboration' | 'affiliate'
  target_audience: string;
  categories: string[];
  geography: string[];
  timeline: string;
  budget: string;
  
  // Metadata
  status: 'draft' | 'active' | 'closed';
  created_at: string;
  updated_at: string;
}
```

